{"tid":1666591,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"移民能圍爐（澳洲專業移民）","createTime":"2019-10-21T04:54:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-10T13:37:40.000Z","uid":250374,"like":5,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"006c464519295a5f5eb5c8373221a3fc6909533a","tid":1666591,"uid":250374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:54:02.000Z","msg":"自我介紹一下，29歲護士，4年RN appt，有意用專業移民visa 189去澳洲<br />\n<br />\n想將「香港」變成一種意識型態，將香港專業人士帶去澳洲繼續發展<br />\n<br />\n有移民諗法其實都有幾年，做過公立醫院既護士一定會明白有幾辛苦，所以希望有能力時去選擇自己想要生活。除此之外就是下一代的未來，希望可以比多個選擇佢。"},{"pid":"baeca9d87b8e2329281de7a3c17a5fdac54b0ad5","tid":1666591,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:54:45.000Z","msg":"不如全港黨鐵靜坐聲討721啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1665580\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1665580</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3c5c09f9c2df4c1a82aafa83981a6ce0bc2a934","tid":1666591,"uid":230973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:57:18.000Z","msg":"英文好難考"},{"pid":"a49719effe086f24eaab12816b27fef95717bd46","tid":1666591,"uid":250374,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a3c5c09f9c2df4c1a82aafa83981a6ce0bc2a934","tid":1666591,"uid":230973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T04:57:18.000Z","msg":"英文好難考"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T05:16:04.000Z","msg":"我知道有幾種考試，其實都係操paper，我自己英文都好差，開一個group就係希望集合一班人，一齊努力，支持"},{"pid":"59eb9e40edbcf8a166b8ce7199eb9cf70cf11298","tid":1666591,"uid":132056,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T05:17:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">天滅中共 全黨死清光</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"5b97c49339a3208c60776d02933a649eff9375e8","tid":1666591,"uid":230973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T05:33:29.000Z","msg":"其實英文差，去到點做"},{"pid":"